PHIT  .  0.30   : Total porosity cutoff
VSH_cut .  0.40 : Shale volume cutoff for net pay
SW_cut  .  0.60 : Sw cutoff for pay
CLAIM  .  EXPLORATORY_VISUALIZATION    : Default claim state
~Other -----------------------------------------------------
BOKOR-1 was drilled by PAPC in March 2024 as a wildcat exploration
well to test Miocene turbidite sands in the BOKOR structural closure.
Result: Gas shows in SS2 and SS3. RFT confirmation pending.
Depths are measured from GL (1235.2m above MSL). All in mMD.
